The hearing screening diagnostic devices market is segmented based on product type, age group, end user, and distribution channel. The market is divided into screening devices and diagnostic devices under product type. In terms of age group, the market caters to both pediatric and adult populations. The end users of these devices include hospitals, specialty clinics, ambulatory surgical centers, and others. Distribution channels for these devices involve direct sales as well as distribution through intermediaries.

